Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.16,0:00:12.36,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,The songs you told me about, Mei-senpai, were all truly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:13.79,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:16.24,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I knew you'd like them, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:18.05,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Did you see the MVs too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:18.96,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:24.80,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Before, I would've felt that MV production should be left to the professionals,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:29.28,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,but that handmade feel from the members is what makes them so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:32.28,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,You can really feel the love for the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:37.36,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,And the pride of being school idols really shines through.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:40.38,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,You get it, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:41.23,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:44.24,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,It's rare to see you two getting so excited together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:45.08,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:46.58,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.36,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:48.84,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.52,0:00:54.56,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Mei-senpai was telling me about some recommended school idols and their songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:56.76,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Kano-senpai, that's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:59.04,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I just thought Yuri might like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:02.76,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,To me, Runa is the absolute best school idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:04.36,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.48,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:07.64,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,It's okay, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:09.60,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:13.80,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,That reaction was like someone caught in the middle of an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:18.32,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,But now I'm curious since you two were so into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.08,0:01:21.46,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Tell me about those school idols too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:22.19,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:34.44,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,No way! I love the lyrics Kano-senpai writes straight from her heart. I love her voice. Her excitement, her worries, her dreams... everything about her is the absolute ultimate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:23.70,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Wait, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:34.95,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:36.74,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:40.76,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,But this person is actually quite easily influenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:41.90,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I just can't stand the thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:46.88,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,of Kano-senpai's unique style changing because of other school idols.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:50.52,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Especially if it happened because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:53.88,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Even if it's just a little bit, I'd hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:57.76,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Is it okay for me to be influenced, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:00.92,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yuri, you wouldn't be swayed by something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:06.36,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Um, Mei-chan, do you trust Yuri-chan more than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:08.40,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I'm your senior, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:14.12,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Well, Mei-senpai, let's save that talk for another time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:16.56,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,and get the radio show started.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:22.04,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Ding-dong-dang-dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:29.72,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Since it's almost April Fools' Day, we've hidden a few lies in our opening talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.72,0:02:33.04,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Everyone, please try to see through our lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.76,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Ding-dong-dang-dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:46.20,3,3,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Musuba Musubi Broadcasting Station: Liella! Radio - Toma, Kano, and Mei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:55.96,3,3,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:01.68,4,4,0,0,0,,I'm Sakakura Sakura, aka Sakuchan, playing Onitsuka Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:02.76,5,5,0,0,0,,Playing Shibuya Kano...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.06,5,5,0,0,0,,I'm Tate Sayuri, aka Saerin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:07.72,6,6,0,0,0,,Playing Yoneme... I'm Yabushima Kano, aka Yabuchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:08.96,3,3,0,0,0,,And we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.16,7,7,0,0,0,,Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:13.68,3,3,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:21.04,4,4,0,0,0,,We've just started, but we're passing through a tunnel right now, so our voices are echoing like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:22.84,6,6,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.72,0:03:24.36,6,6,0,0,0,,The echo is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:24.86,4,4,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:26.65,4,4,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:28.80,5,5,0,0,0,,Nice one, Saku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:29.36,4,4,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:31.60,5,5,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.01,5,5,0,0,0,,Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:33.67,4,4,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.52,6,6,0,0,0,,Sayuri, say something to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.60,4,4,0,0,0,,Yabuyabu, you're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:44.44,4,4,0,0,0,,I love Yabuyabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:45.28,4,4,0,0,0,,I love you, Yabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:46.61,5,5,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.24,5,5,0,0,0,,I love you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:50.75,6,6,0,0,0,,And with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.92,4,4,0,0,0,,we've finally cleared the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.89,0:03:55.61,6,6,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.36,6,6,0,0,0,,What a relief. Truly, truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:57.54,4,4,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:03:58.85,6,6,0,0,0,,I'm so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:09.08,4,4,0,0,0,,Now then, Yabuchan, thanks for being our guest today! Your hair looks lovely, what do you call that style?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:04.10,6,6,0,0,0,,Glad to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:10.68,6,6,0,0,0,,Wait, my hairstyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:18.20,6,6,0,0,0,,Today, I'm wearing my hair down, just like my favorites Sayuri and Sakura often do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.34,6,6,0,0,0,,It's a hairstyle that shows my love for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.20,4,4,0,0,0,,Aww, I love you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:22.99,4,4,0,0,0,,Love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.00,4,4,0,0,0,,Oh my god, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:28.36,4,4,0,0,0,,I love you so much! Oh, by the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:25.76,6,6,0,0,0,,I love you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.36,0:04:33.32,4,4,0,0,0,,Sayuri, I heard you've been into something lately. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:35.34,5,5,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:36.26,5,5,0,0,0,,Listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:37.19,4,4,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.32,4,4,0,0,0,,Hmm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:38.93,4,4,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:39.55,4,4,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:41.00,4,4,0,0,0,,What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:42.11,4,4,0,0,0,,What was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:43.73,4,4,0,0,0,,Housework?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:44.96,4,4,0,0,0,,I've been really into housework lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:49.72,4,4,0,0,0,,I've actually been doing quite a bit of cooking,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:50.22,4,4,0,0,0,,lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:52.36,4,4,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:53.54,4,4,0,0,0,,That's crazy! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:54.32,4,4,0,0,0,,Praise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:55.12,4,4,0,0,0,,Come on, praise me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:55.71,4,4,0,0,0,,That's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.42,6,6,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:59.00,6,6,0,0,0,,That's so cool of you, Sayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.00,4,4,0,0,0,,That's our Sayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.08,5,5,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:00.75,5,5,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:01.33,5,5,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:02.43,5,5,0,0,0,,Speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:06.08,5,5,0,0,0,,Saku-chan, don't you have something you need to tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:08.24,4,4,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:09.96,4,4,0,0,0,,I,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:11.64,4,4,0,0,0,,Sakakura Sakura,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:16.44,4,4,0,0,0,,will be celebrating my birthday in three days, on April 3rd!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:19.92,5,5,0,0,0,,Happy early birthday, Saku-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.24,4,4,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:21.85,6,6,0,0,0,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:23.40,5,5,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:25.58,6,6,0,0,0,,Congrats, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.42,4,4,0,0,0,,Oh my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.10,4,4,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Saku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:28.16,6,6,0,0,0,,Congrats, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.04,4,4,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.96,4,4,0,0,0,,Wait, what? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.18,5,5,0,0,0,,Wait, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.00,5,5,0,0,0,,For now, let's just get into the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.00,5,5,0,0,0,,Alright, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.08,5,5,0,0,0,,Saku-chan, happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:40.73,4,4,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:43.96,4,4,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:46.10,4,4,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.52,4,4,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, dear Saku-chan~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:52.31,4,4,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:52.96,4,4,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:53.53,5,5,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:54.72,5,5,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:56.88,4,4,0,0,0,,And with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.04,4,4,0,0,0,,some real treats have appeared from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:02.36,6,6,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.76,4,4,0,0,0,,You can actually eat these!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:04.99,5,5,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:05.74,5,5,0,0,0,,Aww, they're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:06.56,5,5,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.56,0:06:07.06,6,6,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.26,4,4,0,0,0,,I love the sweets from this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:13.68,4,4,0,0,0,,I'm so glad. These sweets are perfect for you, Saku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:11.78,5,5,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.98,6,6,0,0,0,,A Sakura kitty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.56,4,4,0,0,0,,Since it's cherry blossom season right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:18.06,5,5,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:18.77,6,6,0,0,0,,So many kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.57,4,4,0,0,0,,Kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:20.33,5,5,0,0,0,,Kitties!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:20.99,6,6,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:22.08,4,4,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:23.16,4,4,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.64,4,4,0,0,0,,That surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:35.28,6,6,0,0,0,,So, Sakura, your birthday is coming up on April 3rd. I know it's sudden, but do you have any goals for this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:31.10,4,4,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:36.56,4,4,0,0,0,,I hadn't thought about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.04,6,6,0,0,0,,It's a surprise, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.08,6,6,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:41.16,4,4,0,0,0,,Hmm, what should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:41.67,6,6,0,0,0,,Anything come to mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.12,6,6,0,0,0,,Anything is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:47.18,4,4,0,0,0,,I was actually trying to do an impression of Sayuri just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:48.84,4,4,0,0,0,,but it didn't sound like her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.44,0:06:51.36,6,6,0,0,0,,But I kind of get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:53.38,6,6,0,0,0,,The things you were saying were actually pretty spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.06,4,4,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:54.70,4,4,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:55.38,6,6,0,0,0,,I'm happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.38,0:06:57.26,6,6,0,0,0,,Look, everyone is nodding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:57.96,6,6,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was similar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:06:59.64,4,4,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.10,4,4,0,0,0,,There was definitely a resemblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:05.32,6,6,0,0,0,,It felt like you were just rambling on about nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.70,6,6,0,0,0,,which is kind of my vibe today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.96,4,4,0,0,0,,Did the way I spoke sound like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:10.56,6,6,0,0,0,,You captured her traits well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:11.52,4,4,0,0,0,,Well, that's good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:15.04,4,4,0,0,0,,I wasn't really satisfied with it myself, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:19.04,4,4,0,0,0,,so I want to get to know everyone better and,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:25.32,4,4,0,0,0,,make this a year where I communicate more and get to know everyone even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:26.66,6,6,0,0,0,,That's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.66,0:07:28.84,6,6,0,0,0,,Reflecting on things even in a moment like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:30.68,6,6,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:33.04,5,5,0,0,0,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:39.60,4,4,0,0,0,,Last year, I didn't really get to hang out with the Liella! members much in my private time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:44.94,4,4,0,0,0,,so I hope we can make lots of memories together this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:45.67,6,6,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.76,5,5,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:46.98,4,4,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.26,4,4,0,0,0,,You guys are the first ones to celebrate with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.09,6,6,0,0,0,,Oh wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.70,5,5,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:54.04,4,4,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.36,5,5,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:55.96,5,5,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.46,6,6,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:07:58.92,4,4,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:02.82,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll be talking about the live concert today as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:14.96,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,so let's have a fun show. Please stay with us until the end. Love Live! Superstar!! Musuba Musubi Broadcasting Station: Liellaji! Let's Super Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:05.34,4,4,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:22.92,3,3,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Musuba Musubi Broadcasting Station: Liellaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:30.54,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Once again, I'm Sakakura Sakura, aka Saku-chan, the voice of Onitsuka Tomari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:32.78,5,5,0,0,0,,I'm Date Sayuri, aka Sayurin, the voice of Shibuya Kanon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.54,6,6,0,0,0,,And I'm Yabushima Akane, aka Yabu-chan, the voice of Yoneme Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.52,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:38.42,7,7,0,0,0,,Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:43.48,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Now, it's time for the Yuigaoka Girls' High School Submission Box, where we read your letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:47.04,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Everyone, all together! One, two... Submission Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.52,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Let's introduce the first email.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:50.10,4,4,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:53.26,4,4,0,0,0,,This one is from Liellaji Name: Rodem-sansei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.22,4,4,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.52,5,5,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:58.86,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"Everything about the 7th Live was great,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:02.56,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"but 'Pop Talking' performed by the 2nd-years was especially memorable."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:09.48,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"It's a bright song to begin with, but seeing the four 2nd-years just being their usual selves fit the song perfectly."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:13.60,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"It felt like you were all singing so freely and having a great time."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:19.26,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"Also, seeing Yabushima-san sobbing while talking about this song during the MC was so emotional."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.08,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:21.06,4,4,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:25.32,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Next is from Liellaji Name: Masumasu OK-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.34,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.54,4,4,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:31.32,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"I attended every single performance of the 7th Live for the first time."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:35.82,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"Even with the same songs, every show had something different, and it was so exciting."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:43.58,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"Especially 'Pop Talking'—the four 2nd-years looked like they were having so much fun singing and dancing, like they were having a bright conversation."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.30,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"It was a song that really made me feel the bond between the 2nd-years."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.08,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:48.32,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:49.32,4,4,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:51.48,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Pop Talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:51.98,6,6,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:54.30,6,6,0,0,0,,The four-person version of Pop Talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:58.08,4,4,0,0,0,,It was so cute. And fun! Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.52,6,6,0,0,0,,It really was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.02,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,With Pop Talk-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:06.56,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,ing, the lyrics move so fast from one person to the next, so the hand-offs are really quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.24,0:10:10.56,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,It's like, "Oh, she's singing now! Now it's her turn!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:15.00,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,You don't have enough eyes to keep up, even when we usually sing it at lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:19.28,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,But seeing it performed by just four people felt so fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:26.98,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Because of that, they could walk side-by-side
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:34.36,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,and really look at each other's faces. It felt like four friends walking home together after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:39.00,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,just chatting while they sang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:40.92,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,I really felt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.44,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,I thought so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:52.94,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,It was singing, but it felt more like a conversation. They'd end up laughing because of how the person before them sang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:11:00.72,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Seeing them turn their real-time feelings into words like that was so fun to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:05.16,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,It felt like we were right there participating with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.48,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,It was great to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:17.72,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,The intro to Pop Talking started with all four of them doing Kinako-chan's "Tekuteku Biyori" first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.24,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,They were all in matching outfits too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.52,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,The whole thing felt so special.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:24.90,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:32.56,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Since they were in matching outfits, it really felt like they were heading home after club activities
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:36.58,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,or some other plans they had together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.58,0:11:41.28,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Like, "Let's all go home!" It felt so much like high school girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:43.24,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,I totally agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:44.84,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,That was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:46.90,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,It was adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:48.08,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Man, it was so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:53.44,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,They looked like they were having the time of their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:58.16,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,They said they had a blast, and they were having so much fun backstage too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:00.28,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,I kind of wanted to join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:00.84,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,That's awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.44,0:12:04.06,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,I was so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:06.88,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,I want to sing it with all 11 of us again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:14.28,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,It's a song that really transforms and shines on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.28,0:12:17.20,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,This was the first time the chorus actually had choreography.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:17.83,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.96,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,We never had that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:25.50,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,And they each showed their personality by doing peace signs or blowing kisses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.68,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,For me, I did a bit of a "gyaru" style peace sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:33.92,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,They did peace signs that matched their respective characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.32,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,I don't know if anyone noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:39.70,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,but there was a lot of individuality in those moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:40.68,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Wow, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:42.60,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.60,0:12:43.64,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,They looked so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:47.68,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Everyone, please listen to Pop Talking a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.12,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.28,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Alright, let's keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.96,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Next is from Liellaji Name: Ka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.16,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:56.88,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:00.44,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"I attended Day 2 of the 7th Live in Aichi."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:04.72,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"The song that left the biggest impression on me was Sing! Shine! Smile!."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:10.62,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"Just like the lyrics 'Sing, let's sing together, Smile, connecting our hearts'..."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:15.80,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"Singing this song with everyone made the whole venue feel like one. It was so much fun."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:19.20,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"It reminded me once again that Liella!'s music has so much power."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:23.44,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"Just like the name Yuigaoka suggests, I felt that we are all tied together through song."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:28.10,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"Through the 7th Live, I've come to love Sing! Shine! Smile! even more."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:28.78,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.74,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:30.76,4,4,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:35.04,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,We also have one from Liellaji Name: Nonokura Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.02,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:37.30,4,4,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:42.60,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"Hearing that the 7th Live is recommended even for first-timers,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:45.86,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"I attended my very first live on Day 2 of the Aichi performance."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.45,6,6,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.12,4,4,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:50.84,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"I was completely captivated by everyone's charming performance,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:53.04,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"and the three hours flew by in an instant."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:56.26,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"One thing that surprised me was during Sing! Shine! Smile!,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:58.76,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"when the flow led to everyone singing together."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:03.78,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"At first, I was hesitant, wondering if it was okay to sing along instead of just doing calls."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:08.10,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"But the sense of unity from everyone singing the same song was so fresh and pleasant."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:13.54,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"I felt a connection with everyone in the venue, and it became my best memory."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:15.42,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"Great job on the 7th Live."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:16.76,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,"I'll keep supporting you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:17.86,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,That's the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:18.84,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:20.44,4,4,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that having everyone sing along to this song like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.20,0:14:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't really had many moments like that until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We all put a lot of thought into how to make this happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Nonokura Nonoka-san mentioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,most of our songs usually have 'Hai! Hai!' calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So even with 'Sing Shine Smile,' where the lyrics say 'Let's sing together,'
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,many people were probably wondering, 'Is it okay for me to sing out loud?'
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,or 'How loud should I be singing?' I think there was a lot of hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually saw many people who looked that way. But since the 7th Live was 'Music World,'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we really wanted to showcase Liella! as a group that cherishes singing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and a school that truly values music.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we wanted everyone to sing, and why we chose 'Sing Shine Smile' for the double encore on the final day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the lyrics say 'Let's sing together,'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.48,0:15:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and some people have been singing along for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,there were still many who weren't sure what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're grateful for them, but we really wanted to say, 'Please, sing with us!'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought so much about how to lead them to feel that singing is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to encourage everyone to sing along
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,while still maintaining the immersive world of 'Music World.'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we were aiming for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.76,0:16:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone sang so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and it made me incredibly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, with every performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,more people realized, 'Oh, it's okay to sing!'
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The voices kept getting louder with each show,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was so moved by how the sense of unity grew stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When everyone is singing, we can see your sparkling smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so clearly from the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Those smiles are truly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Singing together makes us smile even more too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For this live, we really wanted to connect our hearts through song more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to make it a concert where everyone could feel that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we all felt that way, I'm so glad we could include songs for everyone to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.68,0:17:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely want to have more opportunities like that in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to keep increasing the number of songs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,where we can all sing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, Liella! has had many songs that are more about 'showing' the performance,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,like 'Aspiration' or 'Jump Into the New World.'
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're performing those, it's more like 'Whoa!'
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't really that kind of back-and-forth interaction
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, 'Sing Shine Smile' was a big challenge for us in a good way,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was so happy that everyone joined in with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:17:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:02.00,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I could really feel that connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.74,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,We felt it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:04.27,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:10.56,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I know some people might still feel hesitant or wonder if it's okay to sing,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:17.92,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,but Sayurin always says 'Please sing along with us' before we start, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:21.76,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Since Kanon-chan says it, when she does,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:28.36,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I hope you'll just sing your heart out without any worries. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:27.60,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.12,3,3,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.84,0:18:31.50,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It was so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:31.42,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:35.76,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Moving on, this next one is from Liella! Radio name, Motocross.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:56.24,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Thank you. 'The first performance of "Orange no Mama de" at the 7th Live was amazing. Putting this song about the sparkle and fleeting nature of youth in the encore was just unfair. Especially on the final day, I couldn't even wave my penlight; I just stood there soaking in that happy moment.'
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:37.84,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:58.36,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:58.34,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:01.96,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Next is from Liella! Radio name, Amatta Neji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:07.68,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Thank you. 'I attended every single performance of the 7th Live. Thank you!'
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:04.00,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:08.35,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:11.42,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,'"Orange no Mama de" is the perfect song for an encore.'
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:18.10,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,'I couldn't watch the part where everyone gathered to strike the same pose as the jacket art without crying.'
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:20.44,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,'Thank you for the best youth ever.'
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:21.14,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.24,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:23.44,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:25.08,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:25.88,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,"Orange no Mama de."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.88,0:19:26.43,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I love it so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:27.73,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,We all love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:30.81,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,It really is a great song.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:31.37,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:36.94,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,It's got those emotional vibes, but how should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:42.08,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,There are parts where we can all get hyped together with everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:49.12,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,and the lyrics are just wonderful. We also put a lot of thought into the jacket photo, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:44.46,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:49.73,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:56.16,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,We adjusted the positions over and over, even by just a tiny bit, because...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:20:01.80,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,the look changes depending on the angle, so we kept...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:15.40,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,going back and forth with the dance teacher. "Tomo-chan, a bit more this way," or "You two, move your faces closer." We did so many fine adjustments. I love that one part.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:13.58,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:25.56,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,The part where our hands are joined and then we slowly layer them... No matter how many times I see it, I love it, but it also feels bittersweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:20.92,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:26.21,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:26.95,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:29.08,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.26,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,That part is adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:56.76,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,It really feels like "after school." Like a normal, everyday after-school moment, but also like a very important after-school for them. The lyrics say "Let's meet again tomorrow," and they probably will meet, but you never really know for sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.10,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:54.09,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:56.60,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.60,0:21:06.20,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,So I really felt the weight of those words, "See you tomorrow." It's just a fleeting moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:04.34,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:09.76,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,but that's how it felt to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.12,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,And for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:23.12,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,for the jacket photo, I find myself imagining what made Kanon and the others—all of Liella—decide to take this photo at that exact moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:31.04,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I wondered who took it, or if they just set up a camera. It was so much fun thinking about that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.60,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,while we were shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:55.68,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,This song feels like "the now that isn't forever." It's packed with that fleeting sparkle unique to school idols and student life. Our costumes were "Aspire" this time, but if they weren't, the vibe would be totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:48.82,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:58.84,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Definitely. Like if we wore school uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:03.08,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Man, if we did it in uniforms, I think I'd actually cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:03.58,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.15,0:22:04.76,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:10.48,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I'm already getting a bit teary just thinking about it. I think wearing the "Aspire" costumes is what's keeping me together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:07.24,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,You were looking a bit teary-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:12.46,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,True, it was for the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:12.99,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:14.40,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:15.26,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.26,0:22:17.08,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Oh no, what if we performed this at a real school?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.83,0:22:22.36,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Ugh, that'd be too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:23.36,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I'd end up squawking like a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.04,0:22:25.18,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,What would I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:25.40,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:26.70,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.70,0:22:33.92,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Part of me wants to do it someday, but another part of me really doesn't. Like, once we do it, it's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:31.62,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:35.52,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,No, I won't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:37.52,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I'm not... I'm not doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:38.04,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I won't. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:38.86,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,No way, I'm not doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:39.80,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I'd be a total wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.84,0:22:42.34,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:42.99,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.99,0:22:44.74,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,All 11 of us as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.74,0:22:45.33,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:47.96,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,It's a song we all love.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:48.44,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,We're so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.96,0:22:49.04,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.08,0:22:53.24,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Next, this is from Rieraji Name Romuromu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:23:01.32,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Thank you! "Congrats on the 7th Live! (Thank you!) This was the first time in my life I was able to attend every single performance."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:55.16,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:02.28,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:06.80,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,"The most memorable part for me was 'Universe,' performed at the Aichi show."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:13.80,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,"The moment the intro started, and when the 2nd and 3rd years waved at me, I couldn't stop crying."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:19.72,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,"I was so happy to be able to sing along with Liella and complete the live performance together."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.72,0:23:22.72,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,"Thank you for such a wonderful and happy time."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.32,0:23:28.26,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,"I live in Aichi, so I'd be very happy if you came back again."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:33.28,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Thank you! Next is from Rieraji Name Romatofu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.32,0:23:30.04,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:44.12,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Thank you. "Congrats on all four shows of Liella! 7th LoveLive! FLY! Music World! (Thank you!) During the encore in Aichi, you performed 'Universe'."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:35.16,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:44.66,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:55.44,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,"The five 1st-generation members used the whole main stage for their performance. I could feel the power and brilliance with my whole body, as if the 'Universe' was right there."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:24:02.28,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,"Combined with the sense of unity from the 'Woah woah' calls, I love this song more and more every time I hear it live."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:07.52,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,"I want to keep layering my voice with Liella's and make even more memories together."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.52,0:24:08.28,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,That's what they wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.28,0:24:09.46,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:12.44,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you! Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.16,0:24:11.76,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:14.00,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Everyone loves "UNIVERSE!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:15.46,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I love it so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.46,0:24:16.71,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It was so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:17.29,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.80,0:24:24.08,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,The cheers were so loud, it felt like everyone had been waiting for "UNIVERSE!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.08,0:24:24.95,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.95,0:24:25.98,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Everyone loves that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.98,0:24:27.88,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,We love it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.68,0:24:28.56,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.88,0:24:28.76,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.56,0:24:30.84,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,How long has it been since we last played it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.84,0:24:32.41,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Has it been a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.41,0:24:33.10,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It has.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.10,0:24:33.64,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.64,0:24:35.96,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,It feels that way, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.16,0:24:35.68,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:43.90,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I was so moved by everyone singing along during the finale.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.90,0:24:45.96,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I even took off my in-ears to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.96,0:24:52.04,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,We extended the length of the "woah-woah" part at the beginning this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.04,0:24:52.36,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.36,0:24:52.93,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.93,0:24:59.64,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Hearing the voices get louder and louder was such a blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.24,0:24:56.74,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.63,0:24:59.19,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.19,0:25:00.18,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.68,0:25:02.14,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Man, that was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.14,0:25:04.28,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,We got to sing on the sub-stage too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.28,0:25:06.92,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,How was it for the 2nd and 3rd gen members?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.12,0:25:05.84,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It was my first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.08,0:25:32.52,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It was so fun! We were so close that I could see everyone's faces clearly. Some people were having a blast shouting "woah-woah," while others were sobbing as they sang. Seeing that almost made me tear up too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.44,0:25:10.12,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,We were so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.52,0:25:35.28,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I think it's really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.28,0:25:51.48,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Moments like that remind me how amazing it is that so many people gather to share the same moment and give so much energy to Liella.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.48,0:25:56.60,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful we could get closer to everyone. It really means a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.76,0:25:56.43,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.43,0:26:05.32,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I feel like as we grow up, we have fewer chances to cry or laugh with our whole hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.32,0:26:16.88,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,compared to when we were kids. So seeing them show us those precious expressions...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.88,0:26:26.48,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,it makes me so happy to think they trust us enough to let out all their emotions like that. That's so true.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.48,0:26:24.98,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.72,0:26:28.84,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I want to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.36,0:26:27.96,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.04,0:26:30.02,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.96,0:26:30.60,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.02,0:26:31.40,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.40,0:26:32.44,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Yeah, I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.04,0:26:47.00,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,The 7th Live really felt like we were creating the songs together with the audience more than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.92,0:26:35.42,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Let's do the "woah-woah" part again!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.99,0:26:47.52,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.52,0:26:48.60,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,There were so many. So many.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.60,0:26:56.48,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,We had so much fun too. We've seen so many people saying they had a great time,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.84,0:26:51.34,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,um...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.48,0:27:00.84,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,but we really had a blast ourselves too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.20,0:27:00.86,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.86,0:27:01.64,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.64,0:27:09.56,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,On Day 1 of the Aichi performance, people probably expected "Mirai no Oto ga Kikoeru" next.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.56,0:27:12.70,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Especially those who had been to the Kanagawa shows
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.70,0:27:16.40,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,and remembered the setlist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.40,0:27:20.62,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,They probably thought "Mirai no Oto ga Kikoeru" was coming up,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.62,0:27:25.24,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,but then I asked the crowd if they could shout "woah-woah" again for the next song.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.24,0:27:27.42,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,That was during Day 1 of the Aichi performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.42,0:27:31.46,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Then, everyone mistakenly thought "Open the Gate" was coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.46,0:27:32.90,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Well, it wasn't exactly a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.90,0:27:43.68,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,A lot of people thought we were doing "Open the Gate" for a third time, so they were all ready to shout, but then "UNIVERSE!!" started.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.68,0:27:50.16,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Doing the same song three times would've been quite a memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.16,0:27:51.96,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,and definitely something new!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.52,0:27:54.12,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,And then, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.12,0:27:58.54,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,A "woah-woah" song came out of nowhere, which was a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.54,0:28:02.68,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,But "Open the Gate" also has a lot of call-and-response,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.68,0:28:05.34,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,just like you were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.34,0:28:08.50,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I'm glad we had so many songs like that this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.50,0:28:09.29,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.29,0:28:10.60,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It was so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.60,0:28:13.20,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I hope we can perform them again. I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.28,0:28:12.78,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.68,0:28:18.24,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Thank you! And thank you all for sending in so many emails.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.08,0:28:15.58,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.36,0:28:19.28,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.28,0:28:22.68,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Now, let's introduce a mail for the "Lunch Time Request" segment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.68,0:28:23.58,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.58,0:28:26.20,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,This one is from "Rieraji Name" Tetsuo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.20,0:28:34.60,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'd like to request "Synshine Smile," which was performed during the double encore of the 7th Live Aichi Day 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.12,0:28:28.04,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.51,0:28:35.16,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.16,0:28:41.34,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I was so happy we could all sing it together with Liella!, so I'd love to hear it during lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.34,0:28:42.20,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.20,0:28:47.20,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,We got that request. Thank you. We read your letter too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.48,0:28:44.32,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.44,0:28:52.48,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,You know, for that double encore, I actually thought we were going to do "Open the Gate" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.48,0:28:58.32,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I was like, "Wait, are we doing Open the Gate three times this time?" but then I heard it was "Synshine Smile."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.32,0:29:01.04,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I thought, "Oh, I guess so. Three times would be a bit much," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.32,0:29:06.22,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,You never know, though. We might do it three times someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.22,0:29:06.92,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,That would be intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.20,0:29:12.26,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Anyway, please have a listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.26,0:29:14.76,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Liella! with "Synshine Smile."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.60,0:29:18.52,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Let's sing together
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.60,0:29:23.56,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Connecting my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.52,0:29:27.80,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Let's make it shine, my
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.72,0:29:31.48,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,star of smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.56,0:29:50.64,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Even if I could go anywhere in the past or future, I'd surely stay right here, savoring this moment with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.84,0:30:02.36,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Small twinkles, one by one, meeting and adding joy, even through the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.40,0:30:09.08,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,...I learned the feeling of fun with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.96,0:30:12.78,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I'm dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.78,0:30:22.36,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I'm just so absorbed, I love it so much I forget to sleep. I don't need freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.75,0:30:24.36,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.36,0:30:26.08,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.64,0:30:35.12,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Even if a night comes where I can't see a thing, I'll find the courage to try and smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.00,0:30:38.68,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,That sparkle is bound to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.23,0:30:40.94,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.94,0:30:42.44,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Smiles sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.41,0:30:45.11,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.11,0:30:46.60,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Everyone's sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.08,0:31:13.04,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell you, so I let my pen glide, and the world smiled as if we were meeting for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.88,0:31:21.64,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I feel like I can grab even the smallest glow, so I reach out my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.40,0:31:25.72,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It was kind of funny, so I burst out laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.56,0:31:31.76,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It's always dazzling, no matter when.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.32,0:31:40.92,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I can do more, I can do more. My heart is pounding uncontrollably.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.04,0:31:43.52,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I won't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.52,0:31:44.19,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Connecting
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.60,0:31:48.16,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,the joy, smiles sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.11,0:31:50.84,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.84,0:31:52.32,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Sparkling with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.04,0:32:14.20,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,We've been put under a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.28,0:32:23.28,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,A spell called a dream that won't end even as time passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.52,0:32:28.48,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It won't break until it comes true.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.48,0:32:28.98,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.88,0:32:36.32,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,No one can stop us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.04,0:32:40.52,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,That's right, we're dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.32,0:32:43.40,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Because I realized
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.08,0:32:47.88,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I don't need freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.56,0:32:57.04,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Even if a night comes where I can't see a thing, I'll find the courage to try and smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.92,0:33:02.92,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,That sparkle is bound to reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.92,0:33:04.36,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Smiles sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.37,0:33:07.09,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.09,0:33:11.16,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Everyone's sparkling, let's sing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.32,0:33:19.80,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Connecting my heart, let's make it shine
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.72,0:33:24.24,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,my star of smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.52,0:33:35.72,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' High School Lunchtime Broadcast Station: Lieradi!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.80,0:33:43.08,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,News from Love Live! Superstar!! regarding Blu-ray info.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.08,0:33:51.88,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,On Wednesday, June 24th, we will release the "Love Live! Superstar!! Liella! 1st Generation Live & Special Live Blu-ray Box."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.68,0:33:56.64,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It includes the Revival Tokyo Day 2 and the Special Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.36,0:34:02.84,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Bonus footage includes behind-the-scenes making-of for both the Revival and Special Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.64,0:34:09.48,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Plus, it comes with a cassette tape of "Shooting Voice" live recordings (1st Gen and 2nd/3rd Gen versions)...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.48,0:34:11.20,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,...and a cast booklet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.04,0:34:18.80,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Also, those who pre-order at target stores by April 15th will receive a cassette-style acrylic keychain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.48,0:34:27.92,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It's a memorial package where you can enjoy the Revival Live tracing the 1st Gen's journey and the one-night-only Special Live, so don't forget to pre-order.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.52,0:34:29.96,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Next is music info.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.76,0:34:36.10,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,On Wednesday, July 8th, the "Liella! Connecting Project Mini Album" will be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.10,0:34:43.64,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,We'll release five versions: Original, Photo, Team Children, Team Sports, and Team Green.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.64,0:34:50.72,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,The Original, Team Children, Team Sports, and Team Green versions feature new illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.72,0:34:53.80,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,The Photo version uses new photos of the cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.52,0:35:01.44,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It's scheduled to include 4 songs, including one new group song, plus off-vocal versions for a total of 8 tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.00,0:35:06.46,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,As a first-press bonus, the Original, Team Children,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.46,0:35:12.56,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Team Sports, and Team Green versions include member stickers, while the Photo version includes purikura-style stickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.48,0:35:22.52,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,All versions include a lottery application ticket for the Love Live! Series 15th Anniversary Love Live! Fes Love Live! Superstar!! presale.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.20,0:35:27.70,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Plus, as a bundle purchase bonus, you'll get a Liella! sticker book.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.70,0:35:29.28,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Don't forget to pre-order.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.92,0:35:34.92,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,To celebrate the release of the "Liella! Connecting Project Mini Album," we'll be holding handover events.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.64,0:35:39.92,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,The dates are Friday, October 2nd and Friday, October 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.64,0:35:44.70,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Those who pre-order or purchase the "Liella! Connecting Project Mini Album" at target stores
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.70,0:35:48.36,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,will be invited to the handover event via lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.20,0:35:54.92,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,The performers vary by date, so please check the application guidelines before applying.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.64,0:35:59.00,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Check the official Love Live! Superstar!! website for more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.54,0:36:00.04,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Next up,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.04,0:36:01.44,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,is the merchandise information.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.44,0:36:09.54,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Pre-orders for the Birthday Present Season 5 Wakana Shiki Set are now open at the Yuigaoka Girls' High School Purchasing Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.54,0:36:20.30,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,It features a new illustration of Shiki-chan in her Lillian outfit, from her solo song on the 3rd album Aspire, which was first performed at the 7th Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.30,0:36:28.72,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Pre-orders are open until 11:59 PM today, Tuesday, March 31st, the day of this Lieradi broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.72,0:36:31.36,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Alright, we have the illustration right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.36,0:36:34.60,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,It's amazing. I'm buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.16,0:36:34.04,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It really suits her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.44,0:36:36.36,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.36,0:36:36.87,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,It looks great on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.29,0:36:39.79,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.79,0:36:40.64,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Mei-chan, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.64,0:36:41.50,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Look at this, Mei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.50,0:36:55.48,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Wow... It's rare to see her in a dress that shows off her legs. I like her in pants too, but she looks like such a delicate girl here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.72,0:36:48.32,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Ah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.76,0:36:58.16,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,True. What's with that face?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.20,0:36:56.70,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.14,0:36:58.64,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.64,0:37:00.48,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,She's got that soft, 'nun' vibe going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.48,0:37:02.64,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Mei-chan... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.44,0:37:01.96,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,As expected of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.76,0:37:08.92,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Should I try to express it like Sayuri would? How's this, Mei-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.92,0:37:05.52,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah, go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.24,0:37:09.88,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,What would she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.88,0:37:10.44,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,If it were Sayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.20,0:37:11.76,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,'I love the emo vibes!'
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.16,0:37:14.64,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,That's all you ever say!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.64,0:37:16.40,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,You literally don't say anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.40,0:37:19.04,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,But it's accurate. It's so accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.24,0:37:18.12,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I'll just say it for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.05,0:37:19.55,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.35,0:37:20.87,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.87,0:37:22.22,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Exactly. Because this is just so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.22,0:37:23.08,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It's super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.83,0:37:24.33,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.48,0:37:27.20,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,'I love it.' It's the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.00,0:37:26.68,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,It really was the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.80,0:37:28.72,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,She's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.32,0:37:35.80,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,This is a made-to-order limited production, so only those who pre-order can get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.80,0:37:40.48,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Check the Liella! official X and the Yuigaoka Girls' High School Purchasing Department for details.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.28,0:37:44.28,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Next is an announcement from the Love Live! Series Official Card Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.80,0:37:49.76,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,On Saturday, May 23rd and Sunday, May 24th, at TFT Hall 1000
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.76,0:37:53.76,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,and TFT Hall 500, we will be holding the Loveca Fan Meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.48,0:38:05.08,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,We'll have early sales of the Love Live! Superstar!! Cheer Up! Start Deck and the Royal Holiday Booster Pack, which officially release on May 30th.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.60,0:38:13.08,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,We'll also have events and exhibits for those who haven't played Loveca yet, so please come visit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.68,0:38:21.00,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Latest info will be posted on the Loveca official website and X, so keep an eye out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.56,0:38:22.64,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Now for appearance information.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.64,0:38:27.16,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Starting April 1st, Liella no Tutorial Season 2 will begin on Nippon TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.16,0:38:31.36,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Time Machine 3-go will continue as the program MCs from Season 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.92,0:38:36.92,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Catch-up streaming will be available on TVer and Nittele Tada after the terrestrial broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.92,0:38:38.56,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Don't forget to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.56,0:38:49.72,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,To celebrate the show, the Love Live! Superstar!! Liella no Tutorial 2026 live event will be held at LaLa Arena TOKYO-BAY on August 1st and 2nd.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.72,0:38:57.16,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,The official second lottery for tickets is currently open on Ticket Pia until 11:59 PM on Sunday, April 5th.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.16,0:38:59.04,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Be sure to check this out as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.68,0:39:05.02,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,For details on all the info we shared today, please check the Love Live! Superstar!! Liella! official X
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.02,0:39:09.06,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,and the Love Live! Superstar!! official website.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.06,0:39:10.48,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,That's all for the announcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.44,0:39:26.44,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,It's almost time to say goodbye on Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' Lunchtime Broadcast Station: Liella!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.44,0:39:28.48,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Here is the information for the next broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.48,0:39:36.76,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,The 267th episode, scheduled for Tuesday, April 7th, will feature Ohkuma Wakana-chan, the voice of Wakana Kinako, as a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.28,0:39:41.40,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Yabu-chan, do you have a message you want to leave for Kuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.40,0:39:43.96,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Let's go out for a meal on your treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.96,0:39:44.55,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.03,0:39:47.68,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.68,0:39:50.52,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,In that case, Saku and I will just watch over you from the shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.52,0:39:51.64,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I wonder what they'll talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.36,0:39:53.58,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,We look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.58,0:39:54.24,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.12,0:39:58.04,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,So, how was today's broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.04,0:39:59.58,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Oh, the birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.58,0:40:02.36,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Happy birthday! I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.28,0:40:01.78,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.28,0:40:04.16,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.16,0:40:04.91,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.56,0:40:08.60,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I'm the first one to say it! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.72,0:40:08.41,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.41,0:40:09.70,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,You really were the first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.70,0:40:10.48,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Yeah, I totally was!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.48,0:40:12.78,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,LieRadio is always the first one to celebrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.78,0:40:14.64,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,every single year. I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.76,0:40:14.26,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.51,0:40:16.01,Yabushima Akane,Yabushima Akane,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.28,0:40:22.80,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,And that's all for this episode of Love Live! Superstar!! Yuigaoka Girls' Lunchtime Broadcast Station Liella!.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.80,0:40:25.10,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,Your hosts were Date Sayuri, the voice of Shibuya Kanon,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.10,0:40:29.04,Sakakura Sakura,Sakakura Sakura,0,0,0,,Sakakura Sakura, the voice of Onitsuka Tomari, and Yabushima Akane, the voice of Yoneme Mei.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.04,0:40:31.24,Date Sayuri,Date Sayuri,0,0,0,,See ya!
